Architecture (High Level)

Civicverse is composed of modular systems, including:
	‚Ä¢	Decentralized identity & vouching
	‚Ä¢	Distributed content persistence
	‚Ä¢	Protocol-level AI governance hooks
	‚Ä¢	Community governance mechanisms
	‚Ä¢	Open documentation and repositories

Each component is designed to function independently and collectively, minimizing single points of failure.

‚∏ª

Ethical AI Governance

Unlike traditional platforms, Civicverse embeds AI ethics at the protocol layer, not as post-hoc policy.

This includes:
	‚Ä¢	Community-defined constraints
	‚Ä¢	Transparent decision logic
	‚Ä¢	Auditable AI behavior
	‚Ä¢	Resistance to covert manipulation

AI within Civicverse exists to serve civilians, not influence or control them.

